channel.title: Nulls nulls nulls
channel.description:
my server has been fine for weeks but one day i logged in and right after i logged in null after null logged in right after i started server
i had 387 nulls online before silab shut off
soo i thought oh maybe its the source.
deleted source
downloaded a new one so i turn on server and bam about 200 nulls log in and server crashes again
every source i tried does this
i even virus scanned and everything seemed to be alright
help me
idk whats going on
i cant play server because of this
ill put up a video to show u
